Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:33.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped along \Nwith the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting\Nthe Donquixote Family fiercely,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:55.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law finally clash with Doflamingo\Nat the Royal Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tragedies that fell on Dressrosa...\NCompared to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is not even pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a ball of the \Nanger of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bring you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half Moon Glaive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that Zoro was keeping off!\NPica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A top executive of the Family shouldn't look\Nso pathetic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Moving Across the Ground!\NThe Giant Statue Pica's Surprise Maneuver!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Bellamy!\NOr you really are gonna kill yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! You bastard!\NYou're still saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again and again!\NYour body's reaching its limit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I decide where I'll die myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna become the King \Nof the Pirates, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't get \Nstalled by crap like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not here to have a one-on-one match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's an enemy,\Nthe fight won't end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself, Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NYou can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means death,\NI have to bring down all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put this country back\Nin the hands of King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is King Riku to you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca. You have been cursed at repeatedly\Nbecause of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros. You lost your leg\Nbecause you were serving him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you were forced to live as a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you! You people framed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} is a \Nfather-in-law and someone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe so much to for taking care \Nof me since I was a bad kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King Riku Family was \Nknown as a venerable family
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that understands the true meaning \Nof peace, even worldwide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country wasn't as wealthy\Nand prosperous as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean \Nthe people were unhappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is clear and\Nflowers are blooming proudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great country filled with gentle hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Dressrosa really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money and jewels are nothing but stones\Nand they have no heart or soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The act of living is true happiness.\NThat is what he told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kicking you bastards out and having \Nhim sit on the throne again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what the whole nation wants now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?! It scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to the third level this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that fool!\NHe's supposed to fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I can't get him\Nif he moves around in the plateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready to die\Nonce you enter my range again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N--Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk! He's harming the injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't cling to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! We're gonna be husband and wife\Nso don't be shy like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed us, Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Mill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're okay! Let me help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you fool! Old man, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pieces of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you fool!\NHow could you mess with the wounded ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bite Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style Demon Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who's on the old King's Plateau?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Former"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your point, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's unfair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invasions always happen in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does only Doffy have to take blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the old King's Plateau,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there aren't only the former \Nsenior officials of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also, those {\i1}samurai{\i0} and God Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the whole nation seeks\NKing Riku's restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pisses me off! Doffy is the only king!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started to move again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What will he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Donquixote's country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna walk! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The statue started to move! Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell... What is he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to kill the king?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!\N--It's gonna crush us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he drove me out this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't catch up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally got played!\NGotta do something or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take him just one punch\Nto shatter the King's Plateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp and the king will be crushed\Nand die in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way to prevent it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter!\NWe won't let you get in Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s way anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way to stop that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plan 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:01.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 1\NLONG-DISTANCE SLASH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Long-distance slash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it has to travel too far \Nso it won't be powerful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take him down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:17.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 2 - JUMP UP AND GET ON TOP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plan 2. Jump up and get on top!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:46.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 3\NSHOUT OUT, WARNING USOPP AND THE OTHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plan 3.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout out, warning Usopp and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way he can hear me from this far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:11.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 4 - CALL HIM BY THE TRANSPONDER SNAIL\NAND TELL HIM "HURRY UP AND RUN"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plan 4.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Call him by the Transponder Snail \Nand tell him "Hurry up and run."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I don't have it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come towards us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can tell him that, there's no \Ntime for all of them to get away anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go for it!\N--Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking to kill King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of our business \Nbut I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You stone monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper King-{\i1}senpai{\i0} is on that plateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stone! Come back here! I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I saved my King Punch\Nas Pirate Hunter told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you now! My friend, King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, you king of somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere?!\NI'm the king of Prodence, Elizabello! Pirate Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's no use just destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll keep coming back\Nunless you beat his flesh and blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we're out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is King Riku there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plan 5.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fly in the sky and chop him up!!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FLY IN THE SKY AND CHOP HIM UP!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLAN 5 - FLY IN THE SKY AND CHOP HIM UP!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:27.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pica's giant fist that almost \Nseems to cover up the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:28.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,comes down onto King Riku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:30.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the lamp of hope that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:33.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,has been lit in Dressrosa is\Nabout to be crushed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:36.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and another age of being ruled \Nby force looms in sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:39.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Pica's final battle breaks out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Decisive Battle in Midair!\NZoro's New Special Secret Technique Blasts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
